Zeep Bot Privacy Policy

1. Introduction
Welcome to Zeep, a Discord bot designed to assist with server moderation and management. This Privacy Policy explains how Zeep collects, uses, discloses, and protects user data. By using Zeep, you agree to the collection and use of information in accordance with this policy.

2. Data Collection
Zeep collects the following types of data to provide its services:

User IDs and Usernames: To identify users and manage interactions.
Message Content: For specific commands such as /clear, /say, and ticket management.
Timestamps: To log interactions and track command usage.
Server and Channel IDs: To identify where commands are executed.
Verification Codes: For user verification processes.
3. Data Usage
The data collected by Zeep is used for the following purposes:

User Management: To manage user interactions, warnings, bans, and other administrative actions.
Service Improvement: To enhance the botâ€™s functionality and user experience.
Security: To ensure the security of the bot and the server.
4. Data Sharing and Disclosure
Zeep does not share or disclose user data to third parties, except in the following circumstances:

With Server Administrators: To manage and enforce server rules.
Legal Requirements: If required by law, to comply with legal processes, or to protect the rights, property, or safety of Zeep, its users, or others.
5. Data Protection
Zeep takes the following measures to protect user data:

Encryption: Data is transmitted using encryption protocols.
Access Control: Data is stored securely and access is restricted to authorized personnel only.
Regular Audits: Regular security audits are conducted to ensure data protection measures are effective.
6. User Rights
Users have the following rights regarding their data:

Access: Users can request access to their data collected by Zeep.
Correction: Users can request corrections to any inaccurate data.
Deletion: Users can request the deletion of their data, subject to administrative needs and legal requirements.
7. Data Retention
Zeep retains user data for as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes outlined in this Privacy Policy. Data may be retained longer if required by law or for legitimate business purposes.

8. Changes to This Privacy Policy
Zeep may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Users will be notified of any significant changes through Discord or other communication channels. Continued use of the bot after changes to the policy will be deemed as acceptance of those changes.

9. Contact Information
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact the server administrators.

